data.description: Well kept Split Foyer in Gambrill's Four Seasons Community.  Updated Kitchen with Stainless Appliances and renovated Bath.  Lower Level has Family Room, Separate Office + a Half Bath and Laundry as well as a 4th Bedroom option.  Freshly Painted Interior and New Carpeting makes it ready for you to move in and enjoy.  Private Back and Side yard back to Nature Preserve offers both privacy and nature views of Odenton Nature Area.  Wide drive for extra parking.  Conveniently located to Commuter Routes, Fort Meade and the Waugh Chapel Swim Club.  An Offer has been received and the offer deadline is this Sunday 2/25 at 4 PM.
